# MoodSpeak AI Library

A creative Python library that detects user emotion and generates AI-powered emotionally aware responses.

Features:
- Emotion detection (happy, sad, angry, excited, neutral)
- Emoji mapping
- AI reply generation with emotion-aware tone
- Simple and easy integration with Flask apps
